#: ../../../glossary.rst:96
msgid "advanced indexing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../glossary.rst:98
msgid ""
"Rather than using a :doc:`scalar <reference/arrays.scalars>` or slice as an "
"index, an axis can be indexed with an array, providing fine-grained "
"selection. This is known as :ref:`advanced indexing<advanced-indexing>` or "
"\"fancy indexing\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../glossary.rst:103
msgid "along an axis"
msgstr ""

